          <h1>Mourad <span>Bouajaja</span></h1>
      <span class="book-tag">Author &middot; Child Protection &middot; Mental Health</span>
      <p class="subtitle">Where other writers approach chess through the lens of competition, I read the board the way a social worker reads a case file: attentive to the structures that shape outcomes, and to the human cost of systems that were never designed with the most vulnerable in mind.</p>
