        <div class="chapter-num">2</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>The Myth of the Mad Genius</h4>
          <p>Paul Morphy, Wilhelm Steinitz, and the origins of a dangerous narrative</p>
        
          <span class="chapter-status in-progress">In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter-card">
        <div class="chapter-num">3</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>Two Endgames: From Fischer to Naroditsky</h4>
          <p>Genius without support, decades apart</p>
        
          <span class="chapter-status in-progress">In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter-card">
        <div class="chapter-num">4</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>The Body at the Board</h4>
          <p>The science of competitive stress in chess</p>
        
          <span class="chapter-status in-progress">In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter-card">
        <div class="chapter-num">5</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>One More Game</h4>
          <p>Digital chess, compulsive play, and the architecture of addiction</p>
        
          <span class="chapter-status in-progress">In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter-card">
        <div class="chapter-num">6</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>The Pattern Seekers</h4>
          <p>Chess and neurodivergence &mdash; a game built for different minds</p>
        
          <span class="chapter-status in-progress">In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter-card">
        <div class="chapter-num">7</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>Medicine on 64 Squares</h4>
          <p>From ninth-century Baghdad to modern prisons: chess as therapy</p>
        
          <span class="chapter-status in-progress">In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter-card">
        <div class="chapter-num">8</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>The Queen's Burden</h4>
          <p>Women, hostility, and the mental health cost of playing in a man's world</p>
        
          <span class="chapter-status in-progress">In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter-card">
        <div class="chapter-num">9</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>The Youngest Pawns</h4>
          <p>Ratings, parents, burnout, and the question of childhood in chess</p>
        
          <span class="chapter-status in-progress">In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter-card">
        <div class="chapter-num">10</div>
        <div class="chapter-info">
          <h4>The Ghost in the Machine</h4>
